ote>政治現實係必然通過，只係時間問題。國教果時，中央無出聲要通過，但今次中央擺明要做。</blockquote><br />\n咩叫政治現實?宜家根本未通過大家已經打定輸數然後咩都唔做</blockquote><br />\n咁做到D咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聚左人先"},{"pid":"92a93cc0fa04df80f731c6429c5f995020bbddef","tid":458611,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政治現實係必然通過，只係時間問題。國教果時，中央無出聲要通過，但今次中央擺明要做。</blockquote><br />\n咩叫政治現實?宜家根本未通過大家已經打定輸數然後咩都唔做</blockquote><br />\n咁做到D咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聚左人先</blockquote><br />\n有D扮現實主義既撚樣不斷阻止人地聚人<br />\n正常一個悲觀既人根本唔會阻住人地咁做<br />\n呢班人目的係咩大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4069c6fb06c28e73332f089b2e75caaded2227","tid":458611,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"會過唔到咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你估我唔想呀"},{"pid":"8f26e5db36aa32528f920916c111a68038e366cc","tid":458611,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會過唔到咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你估我唔想呀</blockquote><br />\n為左阻止條法通過,你願意付出幾多?"},{"pid":"7b224d3fbdc9ec16037feb025966dc405a682ae0","tid":458611,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:39:48.000Z","msg":"高鐵到依家咁多年有邊次打贏到"},{"pid":"7eaa1f3c26929741651a02fd212131c1972aaf20","tid":458611,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好無奈"},{"pid":"bdd06a891c3b7347477166c89a17edccacb7c4e6","tid":458611,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高鐵到依家咁多年有邊次打贏到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國教絕對算一仗勝利"},{"pid":"82ffd92d998b5df3019aa1b7dec545e82a19cc8d","tid":458611,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高鐵到依家咁多年有邊次打贏到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國教絕對算一仗勝利</blockquote><br />\n沒了之鋒帶領<br />\n我們什麼都不是<br />\n<br />\n國教 雨革都係佢搞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e577258c03d221a1025c038842a08633d0c0029","tid":458611,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"乜唔係入左附件三就唔駛過立法會咩？"},{"pid":"637cee9c71641e77a6a2a07f939eeb30e9a473ac","tid":458611,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"我好人D<br />\n幫個比一球我，我就令佢立唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快D課水比我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e993ef51a9bcfe183cd67c148726177477d7450","tid":458611,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高鐵到依家咁多年有邊次打贏到</blockquote><br />\n魚蛋"},{"pid":"00ee19b9ca8c49839b7e4532000997502cade5b9","tid":458611,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"網絡23條算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b85601a9969bf7f542de0b65a0fffacd370a581","tid":458611,"uid":74763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"證明之前不停拉低香港人底線十分成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次d政策都係十分惡啃，然後有班人就提出d無咁難頂既方法愚弄市民接受，加多少少修訂就當惡法無問題。嗱！中共要人食成舊屎咁無人性，我地要食半舊，仲要落胡椒粉既。<br />\n<br />\n鬼唔知佢強行通過一定通到咩。反抗係會攰係會令人氣餒，但就係要增加對方既成本，唔駛下下推得咁容易。你每次反抗下，令佢受小小阻礙，佢都無咁易當你臭雞啦。下下都將共產黨派解放軍打鳩香港掛口邊，咁就乜鳩都唔駛做。唔好消極到次次自動訓底張開腿，然後諗住帶耳機聽下歌俾人強姦既時間好快過先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    咁易上，下次要解決性慾第一時間諗起你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b39f80a512057be5faf50b0aa496627a6806580","tid":458611,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜唔係入左附件三就唔駛過立法會咩？</blockquote><br />\n成件事立法會只可以行立法果個程序"},{"pid":"60877d3ba2fddde8c3e72b69de33ffe4fe7e7baa","tid":458611,"uid":6263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為知道一定會成功強行立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成功立法係因為大家都唔反抗，係個結果<br />\n而唔係個原因</blockquote><br />\n反抗過，但係有分別咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e596d5ab5d60abbbbd94d2f8d736f1aaae51b937","tid":458611,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"終於有人講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808d5b3e0944bf142ae5298dcf2c50b9ad1ad812","tid":458611,"uid":36445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗定plan b都有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係你無plan a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c012f3115b849abdfe5db7a6232e928c636570d","tid":458611,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為知道一定會成功強行立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成功立法係因為大家都唔反抗，係個結果<br />\n而唔係個原因</blockquote><br />\n反抗過，但係有分別咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新年你仲有得出mk食魚蛋呢d 雖然係小事 但如果唔係落場打過，呢個文化一早無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時d野係你贏左都唔覺，因為我地起初過得太好，自動當左呢d 野係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915